{{Top|leg}}
'''VicksVisc''' was a company that manufactured casings for [[Holoprojector/Legends|holoprojectors]]. They were used on the [[R2-series astromech droid/Legends|R2-series]] of [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]], namely [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]].

==Behind the scenes==
The company was named for Vickers Viscount, the airplane from which a reading lamp was used for the holoprojector casing.

